<item>
            <title>[LU-15010] grant shrink for MDTs</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15010</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Implement the grant shrink mechanism for MDC-&amp;gt;MDT connections, in the same manner as OSC-&amp;gt;OST connections. There is already an existing &lt;tt&gt;OBD_CONNECT_GRANT_SHRINK&lt;/tt&gt; flag, so this could be added without affecting interoperability.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It would be desirable to include this into 2.15.0 if it is not too complex.  &lt;/p&gt;</description>
